                "<strong>☐ Request 3-4 removal quotes</strong> from established Staffordshire providers. Surveyed quotes only — phone quotes for any home over 1-bed are almost always wrong.",
                "<strong>☐ Decide packing service tier:</strong> full, fragile-only, DIY, or materials-only. See <a href='professional-packing-services-staffordshire-2026.html'>our packing service guide</a>.",
