                "Beyond standard flat removals we offer <a href='../services/man-and-van.html'>man-and-van service</a> for the smallest flat moves, <a href='../services/student-removals.html'>student removals</a> for the Keele University student housing market, <a href='../services/storage-services.html'>storage</a> for between-completion gaps, and <a href='../services/packing-services.html'>professional packing</a> as add-ons. <a href='../areas-covered/removals-newcastle-under-lyme.html'>Our Newcastle-under-Lyme page</a> covers the Keele student flat market specifically. <a href='../reviews.html'>Customer reviews</a> include many flat-move customers across Staffordshire.",
